stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> INIT
    INIT --> IDLE
    IDLE --> GENERATE: START
    GENERATE --> STORE
    STORE --> GENERATE: índice < 15
    STORE --> READ: índice = 15
    READ --> PROCESS
    PROCESS --> READ: índice < 15
    PROCESS --> FORMAT: índice = 15
    PROCESS --> ERROR: overflow
    FORMAT --> TX
    TX --> DONE: fim da UART
    DONE --> GENERATE: novo START
    ERROR --> GENERATE: novo START
